response.overview: Start your engines! Because we're racing as part of the DisneylandÂ® Resort 70th Celebration! Take a scenic and high-speed ride through Radiator Springs Racers in this immersive Point of View adventure. Tour Ornament Valley and arrive in Radiator Springs, the cutest little town in Carburetor County! From the roar of the engines to the charming Cadillac Range mountains, this Cars Land attraction has the perfect blend of heart and horsepower. Every twist, turn, and rev of the engine will have you experiencing the joy of seven decades of Disney imagination and innovative storytelling at top speed!
response.tagline: Prep for the big race with this Point of View adventure though Radiator Springs Racers!
